name: @storybook/postinstall

5.3.0-alpha.45.name: @storybook/postinstall
5.3.0-alpha.45.description: A minimal utility library for addons to update project configurations after the addon is installed via the [Storybook CLI](https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook/tree/master/lib/cli), e.g. `sb add docs`.
